<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HTML Lists Example</title>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container">
        <section>
            <h2>Unordered List</h2>
            <p>Commonly used for bulleted items:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Front-end Development</li>
                <li>Back-end Development</li>
                <li>Full-stack Development</li>
                <li>UI/UX Design</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Ordered List</h2>
            <p>Used for steps or ranked items:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Plan the project</li>
                <li>Design the wireframes</li>
                <li>Write the code</li>
                <li>Deploy to the server</li>
            </ol>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Lists with Different Markers</h2>

            <p>Alphabetical (Ordered):</p>
            <ol type="A">
                <li>First Option</li>
                <li>Second Option</li>
            </ol>

            <p>Square Bullets (Unordered):</p>
            <ul style="list-style-type: square;">
                <li>Red</li>
                <li>Blue</li>
                <li>Green</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

    </div>

</body>

</html>